name: Extraordinary Events of Gary Cartlidge x Aeneas Middleton

metadata.name: I Wont Do It Again (A Gamblers Identity)
metadata.description: This is the real me, laying there, beaten in the matrix of nothingness pursuing favorite numbers in the last of human errors and "random" outcomes. I wont do it again, sometimes you have to fall before you can rise and this time i fell hard. Now you all see my true colors and identity.  This is a mix media piece, photography, digital paint and illustrated elements. mp4 3000 x 2000 -  Music by Multi-Platinum producer Aeneas "Hardley Davidson" Middleton
